description: Some clubs are just born dirty. Others have it thrust upon them. In this smutty Grindhouse, anything goes. NakedSword Originals takes you on an uncensored journey into the dark recesses of San Francisco strip clubs - a world where success can require a good deal more than dancing. In the premiere episode, Seth Knight aches for a stage slot in Trenton Ducati's infamous club. He may not have all the moves, he's sure he's got the right ones. After sneaking past the desk clerk (Christian Wilde), Seth descends into the bowels to audition for gruff stage manager Trenton Ducati. But when Seth blows the audition, he does what comes naturally - and auditions to blow. Trenton takes him up on his offer - and then some! - but will it be enough to get him the spotlight? Find out why there's not a light red enough for Grindhouse.
title: Grindhouse
